original_title: Iron Man Pro XVI Bodybuilding Championship 2005
overview: Complete coverage of the 2005 Iron Man Pro XVI Bodybuilding Championship showcases an impressive lineup of well-oiled physiques, including those of medal winners Lee Priest, Troy Alves, Melvin Anthony and first-time champion Gustavo Badell. Among the highlights are each competitor's posing routine and the ultimate "pose-down," plus the presentation of a lifetime achievement award to sports activist Jim Lorimer.
title: Iron Man Pro XVI Bodybuilding Championship 2005
